secubox-netdiag (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release — Network Diagnostics Module
  * FastAPI backend with 16 endpoints
  * Tools: ping, traceroute, DNS, WHOIS, MTR, nmap, portscan
  * Network info: interfaces, routes, ARP, connections
  * Bandwidth testing via iperf3
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend
  * Tabbed interface: Tools, Interfaces, Routes, Connections
  * Terminal-style output display
  * Security: Port scanning restricted to local network

